    "image_with_text_h44Meb": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "caption_UJ3hny": {
          "type": "caption",
          "settings": {
            "caption": "5 Little Monkeys",
            "text_style": "subtitle",
            "text_size": "medium"
          }
        },
        "heading_T8DB3b": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Inspired by Our Children & a Simple Love for Sleep",
            "heading_size": "h3"
          }
        },
        "text_FXjDqz": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p> When our daughters were ready to leave their cribs and move into their first big girl beds, we discovered there was not a mattress on the marketplace specifically designed for the needs of children. This was a shock to us because our family has been in the bedding business for over 70 years, and we were amazed we had never noticed this glaring need in the market. </p><p>Simply put, the bedding industry has never made children's mattresses a priority. The choices for children's mattresses have been quality mattresses designed with adults in mind, or poor quality mattresses that are passed off as \"good enough for kids.\" We knew how important sleep was for proper mental and physical development, so we wanted something better for our daughters. With our expertise in the bedding industry and a few years of parenting under our belt, we set out to create the ideal sleep system bed for kids. We spent months testing materials, creating layouts, and tweaking designs until we found all the best components needed in a kids mattress that helped our daughters get to sleep faster, sleep more soundly through the night, and waking up feeling rested, refreshed, and healthy. The result is the revolutionary 5 Little Monkeys Sleep System bed - and we are beyond excited to share it with you and your family.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "button_xbDinH": {
