    "image_with_text_XhynRD": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "caption_ejnEQb": {
          "type": "caption",
          "settings": {
            "caption": " A Long History of Quality Bed Makers",
            "text_style": "subtitle",
            "text_size": "medium"
          }
        },
        "heading_8aNfT4": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Behind Your 5 Little Monkeys' Kids Mattress",
            "heading_size": "h3"
          }
        },
        "text_jLcixe": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Once upon a time, in 1945, there was a bed maker named Irving Harrow who founded a small company called Hollywood Bed. He would hand make his beds until they were just right. Each afternoon, he would load up what he made that morning in his station wagon and deliver them to his customers.</p>\n\n<p>When Irving's son Larry rose to the helm in the 1970s, Hollywood Bed grew its capabilities and product line. He invested in state-of-the-art equipment and demanded only the finest bedding products in the industry.</p>\n\n<p>In 1997, Larry's son, Jason Harrow, started working at the company and took over the operation in 2010. He further grew the company to supply some of most significant retailers and hotel brands in the world, while keeping quality as the #1 priority. Inspired by their two girls, Jason and his wife Courtney decided to create the ideal sleep system bed for kids...and 5 Little Monkeys was born! Today, we provide toddler mattresses for children throughout the country!</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "caption_ejnEQb",
