        "heading_ncRFpd": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Kids & Toddlers Today",
            "heading_size": "h3"
          }
        },
        "text_mdtfAa": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The 5 Little Monkeys Mattress bed is the result of years of study and work spent perfecting a mattress designed specifically for kids. If you're ready to find out the difference that better sleep can make in your child's life, we're excited to show you. Try our toddler mattress risk-free today: if you aren't completely in love with it after 100 nights, we'll give you a full refund, no questions asked. Give your child the gift of better sleep - order <b>our children's sleep system bed </b>today!</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
